I'm pleased to announce the release of bzr 0.14. This release is stable
and suitable for general deployment.

Tarballs:
    http://bazaar-vcs.org/releases/src/bzr-0.14.tar.gz
and GPG signature:
    http://bazaar-vcs.org/releases/src/bzr-0.14.tar.gz.sig

