ce
      and correctness as part of the dirstate development. (Robert Collins,
      John A Meinel, Martin Pool, and others).

    * For users of bzrlib: The attribute 'tree.inventory' should be conside=
red
      readonly. Previously it was possible to directly alter this attribute=
, or
      its contents, and have the tree notice this. This has been made
      unsupported - it may work in some tree formats, but in the newer dirs=
tate
      format such actions will have no effect and will be ignored, or even
