Hi,

I've just uploaded a disk image that features Bazaar 1.0 final installer
for the Mac platform.

There's a wiki page dedicated to the installer:
http://bazaar-vcs.org/MacOSXBundle

Some highlights from that page...

Contents of the package:
 - Bazaar 1.0 (library and executable)
 - PyCrypto 2.0.1 and Paramiko 1.7.1
 - BzrTools 1.0.0
 - QBzr 0.8.0
 - Rebase plugin 0.3
 - Documentation in PDF format (installed as well, but can be accessed
from the disk image directly)

Download:

