On behalf of QBzr developers team I'd like to announce release of QBzr 0.11.
Main goal of this release is to provide version of QBzr compatible with changes
made in bzr 1.16.

What's in this release
----------------------
Maintenance release: compatibility with bzr 1.16 (bencode releated changes),
improved performance of qlog, more fixes for side-by-side qdiff, a dozen of
various bugfixes.

