We've just released the first version of the bzr-hg plugin. This plugin
(like the bzr-svn and bzr-git plugins) provides direct support in Bazaar
for accessing Mercurial repositories.

This is the initial version of the plugin, so please use with care. It
may eat your cat or (more likely) destroy your data. The mappings will
definitely change in the near future, so please don't use for production
branches yet.

