The Bazaar development team is happy to announce availability of the
second release candidate for bzr 2.0.0.  We expect to release 2.0.0 within
a week, with no code changes from this rc, and we would very much
appreciate testing and bug reports on this release.

The focus of this release is our new repository format, 2a, which becomes
the default in the 2.0.0 release.  This release fixes some important bugs
in the first release candidate so we recommend people using 2.0rc1
upgrade.  This release is now also suitable for use by users of earlier
bzr releases.

Starting from 2.0.0 we will maintain a stable series of 2.0.x releases,
with no api or format changes, only bug fixes. =20

Source and binaries for this release are now available from
<https://launchpad.net/bzr/2.0/2.0.0rc2>, and the changes since 2.0.0rc1
are summarized below.

