    files. (#456849, Jelmer Vernooij)

 PERFORMANCE

  * Don't import head revision twice when pulling from Git.
    (Jelmer Vernooij)

 FEATURES

  * Support (dumb) HTTP repositories. (#373688, Jelmer Vernooij)

  * Implement API for colocated branches. (#380871, Jelmer Vernooij)

