   * Better compatibility with bzr 2.6+: fixed warning message
     `Cannot expand "commit_data": Dicts do not support option expansion`.
     (Alexander Belchenko, Bug #1254838)

Tarball is on the page https://launchpad.net/qbzr/0.23/0.23.2

For Windows users I strongly suggest to get copy of plugin by branching it
with command

bzr branch lp:qbzr

into directory with your plugins.

Have a nice day,
Alexander

